OL,7,FA shoplifter who stole #60,000 worth
OL,8,Fof products from numerous Boots stores
OL,9,Fhas been jailed for four years.
OL,11,FAlexandru-Iulian Dima, 25, travelled
OL,12,Fthe length and breadth of the UK on
OL,13,Fhis crime spree, but it came to an end
OL,14,Fwhen plain-clothed police officers
OL,15,Farrested him in Pontypridd.
OL,17,FSouth Wales Police said officers had
OL,18,Fmounted a sting operation, believing
OL,19,Ftheir town would soon be targeted by
OL,20,Fthe travelling criminal.
