OL,7,FStaff at the Boots store spotted Dima
OL,8,Finside their shop and alerted police
OL,9,Fusing a radio system used by retailers
OL,10,Facross the town, which gives them
OL,11,Fdirect access to patrolling officers.
OL,13,FDima made a run for it but couldn't
OL,14,Fevade officers, who caught him in a
OL,15,Fnearby car park.
OL,17,FIt brought an end to a campaign of
OL,18,Fshoplifting across the UK. In just 12
OL,19,Fmonths, he stole #60,000 worth of
OL,20,Fproducts from Boots stores in Wales,
OL,21,FEngland and Scotland.
