OL,7,FOn Thursday, 8 August, he was jailed
OL,8,Fat Cardiff Crown Court for four years
OL,9,Fafter earlier pleading guilty to 32
OL,10,Fshoplifting offences.
OL,12,FA deportation order means he will
OL,13,Freturn to Romania immediately after he
OL,14,Fis released, police said.
OL,16,FPC Liam Noyce: "We looked at intel
OL,17,Faround his offending and chose the day
OL,18,Fwe believed he'd come to town.
