OL,7,F"Lo and behold, we had the call from
OL,8,Fstaff at Boots and we arrested him,
OL,9,Fbringing an end to the campaign of
OL,10,Fcrime committed in towns and cities
OL,11,Fthe length and breadth of the UK.
OL,13,F"We understand how vital retailers
OL,14,Fboth large and small are to the town
OL,15,Fand are determined and committed to
OL,16,Fensure they are protected from
OL,17,Fcriminality."
